show.title: Say I Love You When We Meet Again
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/5KdbfR
show.description: To ensure that Caius can have a heart operation, Freya had no choice but to part ways with him. Consequently, Caius came to despise Freya. At the same time, Caius' mother took away the boy born to Freya. Six years later, due to a fight between Freya's daughter and her classmate, Freya met Caius again. Thereafter, they were drawn into a painful and tormented love relationship characterized by alternating emotions of love and hatred.
